## Import

API keys can be imported using their canonical:

```shell
terraform import cycloid_organization_api_key.example my-api-key-canonical
```

> **Note:** After import, the `token` attribute will be empty in state (the API does not expose the token after creation). The resource functions correctly for all other operations, but the token value will not be available.
